def test_myhome_business_create_others_character_specification(self):
        try:
            # 初始化我的主页个人说明书状态为商务
            self.test_myhome_business_status_change()

            self.page.wait_for(
                lambda: self.page.element_is_exists(selector=myhome_friendship_create_other_tag,
                                                    inner_text=myhome_friendship_create_other_inner_text,
                                                    max_timeout=max_timeout),
                max_timeout=max_timeout)
            time.sleep(3)

            # 点击为他人创建
            create_btn = self.page.get_element(selector=myhome_friendship_create_other_tag,
                                               inner_text=myhome_friendship_create_other_inner_text,
                                               max_timeout=max_timeout)
            create_btn.tap()

            # 选择 文字转说明书
            create_other_list = self.page.get_elements(myhome_friendship_create_other_title_element,
                                                       max_timeout=max_timeout)

            if len(create_other_list) != 4:
                self.logger.warning(f"预期4个元素，实际找到 {len(create_other_list)} 个")

            for item in create_other_list:
                if item.text == myhome_friendship_create_other_character_specification_name:
                    item.tap()

            self.page.wait_for(
                lambda: self.page.element_is_exists(home_create_other_title_element, max_timeout=max_timeout),
                max_timeout=max_timeout)
            time.sleep(3)

            # 随机生成1-5字姓名
            self.logger.info("生成随机文本内容...")
            random_name = random_text_generator.generate_random_text(
                min_len=1,
                max_len=5,
                chinese_ratio=1  # 80%中文+20%英文
            )
            self.logger.info(f"生成随机文本（长度：{len(random_name)} 字）：{random_name}")
            # 姓名随机
            # name = "李白白"
            name = random_name

            """手机号"""
            # 手机号随机
            phone = RandomPhone.random_phone()

            text = f"{name}{phone}微信同号\n上海福芮柚科技有限公司创始人\n《FreeTrust》创造者\nshaokunlun@freeuuu.com\n北京大学2025级法律系\n上海市人工智能学会执行副秘书长\n#公众号：FreeTrust商务社交圈"

            time.sleep(2)

            # 输入到输入框
            self.logger.info("向输入框输入内容...")
            input_box = self.page.get_element(home_create_other_character_specification_text_element,
                                              max_timeout=max_timeout)
            input_box.input(text)
            self.logger.info("文本输入成功")

            # 验证输入内容是否正确
            inputted_text = input_box.attribute("value")
            assert inputted_text == [text], f"输入内容不一致：预期{[text]}，实际{inputted_text}"
            self.logger.info("输入内容验证成功")

            # 点击开始识别
            start_btn = self.page.get_element(home_create_other_character_specification_start_element,
                                              max_timeout=max_timeout)
            start_time = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
            start_btn.tap()

            while True:
                end_btn = self.page.element_is_exists(home_create_other_character_specification_end_element,
                                                      max_timeout=max_timeout)
                if not end_btn:
                    end_time = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
                    break

            total_time = int(end_time) - int(start_time)
            self.logger.info(f"AI 识别消耗的时间为：{total_time} 秒")

            # 检查必填项 姓名输入框
            name_value = self.page.get_element(home_create_other_character_specification_name_element,
                                               max_timeout=max_timeout)
            if name_value.value == "":
                name_value.input(name)

                # 验证输入内容是否正确
                inputted_text = name_value.attribute("value")
                assert inputted_text == [name], f"输入内容不一致：预期{[name]}，实际{inputted_text}"
                self.logger.info(f"自动填充姓名失败，手动添加成功：{inputted_text} ")

            # 检查必填项 手机号输入框
            phone_value = self.page.get_element(home_create_other_character_specification_phone_element,
                                                max_timeout=max_timeout)
            if phone_value.value == "":
                phone_value.input(str(phone))

                # 验证输入内容是否正确
                inputted_text = phone_value.attribute("value")
                assert inputted_text == [str(phone)], f"输入内容不一致：预期{[str(phone)]}，实际{inputted_text}"
                self.logger.info(f"自动填充手机号失败，手动添加成功：{inputted_text} ")

            create_btn = self.page.get_element(home_create_other_character_specification_btn_element,
                                               max_timeout=max_timeout)
            create_btn.tap()

            for i in range(10):
                if self.app.current_page != find_create_other_detail_page_url:
                    time.sleep(1)

            if self.app.current_page == find_create_other_detail_page_url:
                self.logger.info(f"文字转名片创建个人说明书成功_用户名：{name} _手机号：{phone}")
                timestamp = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
                self.capture(f"文字转名片创建个人说明书成功_用户名：{name} _手机号：{phone}_{timestamp}.png")
            else:
                timestamp = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
                self.capture(f"文字转名片创建个人说明书失败，请手动检查_{timestamp}.png")
                assert self.app.current_page == find_create_other_detail_page_url, f"文字转名片创建个人说明书失败，请手动检查"

        except Exception as e:
            self.logger.error(f"文字转名片创建个人说明书失败：{str(e)}")
            # 异常时截图
            timestamp = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
            self.capture(f"文字转名片创建个人说明书失败，请手动检查_{timestamp}.png")
            raise

        time.sleep(2)
